# 🟡 9. ELECTRON (DESKTOP APP)

## 🔹 What is Electron?

👉 Converts web app into desktop app

---

## 🔹 HOW YOU USED IT

👉 You created:

```plaintext
main.js
package.json
```

---

## 🔹 WORKING

```plaintext
Electron → opens → http://localhost:8081
```

---

## 🔹 FLOW

```plaintext
User → Electron Window → Spring Boot → H2 DB
```

---

## 🔹 WHAT HAPPENS

1. Electron starts
2. Backend runs (Spring Boot)
3. Electron opens browser window
4. Loads your web app

---

## 🔹 RESULT

✔ Looks like real software
✔ No browser required
✔ Desktop experience

---

# 🟡 10. IMPORTANT POINTS ABOUT ELECTRON

✔ Uses Chromium browser
✔ Uses Node.js
✔ Runs local server inside app

